<h1>Custom branded iPads lead to more engaging events.</h1>
<h3><strong>Overview</strong></h3>
An association aimed at meeting the challenges of exploration and production in the oil, gas and renewable resources industry holds events to educate 110,000 members across 141 countries.
<h3><strong>Their results</strong></h3>
<ul>
	<li><strong>A high volume of iPad check-outs and check-ins processed in an organized, efficient way.</strong></li>
	<li><strong>Sponsored content in the hands of 300 audience attendees.</strong></li>
	<li><strong>100% of iPads returned and undamaged.</strong></li>
</ul>
<h3><strong>What they needed</strong></h3>
They needed an interactive way to get people engaged with sponsored content during their event. They were concerned about their liability when handing out rented devices to attendees and needed an inventory process.
<h3><strong>What we delivered</strong></h3>
We custom branded and imaged 300 iPads. We provided charging stations to keep them fully powered during the event and on-site technicians who managed inventory control. The technicians used bar code readers to link attendees to iPads making sure all iPads were returned undamaged at the end of the event.

